I'm looking to buy anyone's used MagPul PMAGs or Hex Mags. Any generation, any color. I don't care if they're all dirty and dinged up, as long as they work. No more than $10 each. Top dollar goes for 30 round, black, windowed magazines. I am willing to buy in bulk as well. The more you have, the farther I'm willing to drive.

The only restrictions I have are to drums, 10/30, 15/30 or any other pinned mags.
